OL,3,CPatients dying alone amid hospital
OL,4,Cnursing shortages ` RCN survey
OL,6,FHospital patients are being left to
OL,7,Fdie alone because of staff shortages,
OL,8,Faccording to a new report.
OL,10,FThe Royal College of Nursing (RCN)
OL,11,Fsaid its research suggested that only
OL,12,Fa third of shifts had enough
OL,13,Fregistered nurses on duty.
OL,15,FNurses are often caring for dozens of
OL,16,Fpatients at a time, said the RCN, as
OL,17,Fit called for safety-critical limits
OL,18,Fon the maximum number of patients a
OL,19,Fsingle nurse can be responsible for.
