OL,3,CPatients dying alone amid hospital
OL,4,Cnursing shortages ` RCN survey
OL,6,FA survey of more than 11,000 nursing
OL,7,Fstaff found many were demoralised from
OL,8,Fbeing unable to keep patients safe,
OL,9,Fthe RCN said.
OL,11,FOnly a third of hospital nursing staff
OL,12,Fsaid their shift had the planned
OL,13,Fnumber of registered nurses on it.
OL,15,FSignificant numbers in accident and
OL,16,Femergency and outpatient departments
OL,17,Freported having more than 51 patients
OL,18,Fto care for.
