OL,3,CPatients dying alone amid hospital
OL,4,Cnursing shortages ` RCN survey
OL,6,FA nurse working in the community in
OL,7,Fthe south-west of England, said: "We
OL,8,Fhave days when we have 60 visits
OL,9,Funallocated because we don't have
OL,10,Fenough staff.
OL,12,F"Every day we are asked to do more. We
OL,13,Fare always rushing."
OL,15,FAnother, also working in the community
OL,16,Fin the south of England, said: "We
OL,17,Fleave over 50 patients requiring
OL,18,Fnursing care unseen on a daily basis
OL,19,Fdue to poor staffing levels. This
OL,20,Fleads to increases in hospital
OL,21,Fadmissions and death.
