OL,6,F"It is left to us to decide who gets
OL,7,Fseen and who gets missed, which is
OL,8,Fheartbreaking."
OL,10,FIn a hospital in the West Midlands one
OL,11,Fnurse, said: "I have not been able to
OL,12,Fsit with patients who are dying,
OL,13,Fmeaning they have been left to die
OL,14,Falone.
OL,16,F"I have not had the time to make sure
OL,17,Fpatients are fed properly and have
OL,18,Fadequate drinks."
