OL,6,FA midwife, working in a hospital in
OL,7,FYorkshire, said: "Completely unsafe
OL,8,Fcare due to unacceptable staffing
OL,9,Flevels. The standards of what is
OL,10,Facceptable care for a service to
OL,11,Fprovide have fallen so low, the
OL,12,Fbenchmark is survival."
OL,14,FRCN acting general secretary Professor
OL,15,FNicola Ranger said: "In every health
OL,16,Fand care setting, nursing staff are
OL,17,Ffighting a losing battle to keep
OL,18,Fpatients safe.
