OL,3,CPatients dying alone amid hospital
OL,4,Cnursing shortages ` RCN survey
OL,6,F"Without safety-critical limits on the
OL,7,Fmaximum number of patients they can
OL,8,Fcare for, nurses are being made
OL,9,Fresponsible for dozens at a time,
OL,10,Foften with complex needs.
OL,12,F"It is dangerous to patients and
OL,13,Fdemoralising for nursing staff.
OL,15,F"When patients cannot access safe care
OL,16,Fin the community, conditions worsen
OL,17,Fand they end up in hospital where
OL,18,Fworkforce shortages are just as
OL,19,Fsevere. This vicious cycle fails staff
OL,20,Fand patients ` it cannot go on.
